    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unnerve your spell’s victim with odd gestures, cackling laughter, or other effects.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Cha 15, Intimidate 5 ranks, ability to cast spells.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: As a reaction when a creature fails a saving throw against a spell you cast this round, you can attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize that creature. You can target only one creature regardless of how many creatures your spell affected, and a given creature can’t be targeted by this ability more than once per day.</span></p>",
